rComments: She is not a good lecturer but has a very specific way of teaching economics. She uses her own definitions for economics vocab and those specific definitions will come up on the tests. Overall found what she'd say in class to be really difficult to follow. Her slides only cover a little bit of what's on the myeconlab quizzes so you're better off making notes from myeconlab or the textbook. You can tell she's a nice person who cares about the students but her teaching method definitely isn't all there
